textAfterTable: The workshop that Mitch & Jimmie is giving on this Workshop Tour: Variety of Cool Kits Who:                        All ages, all skill levels! -- Anyone and everyone can learn to solder and make cool things with electronics! Workshop timing:  About 3 hours for the workshop, 2 hours setup time before the workshop, 1 hour cleanup after the workshop. Cost:                        Kit prices range from £10 to £25 (see below for kits and prices). More Info                (This workshop is similar to what Mitch does every Monday when in home at Noisebridge, in San Francisco):          https://www.noisebridge.net/wiki/Circuit_Hacking_Mondays Kits!
